Body Types
-Parasite(tiny, mindcontrol)
-Humanoid(human like)
-Colony(many smaller)
-Fleshy Mass(normal)

Lair Stats
Defence - Likelyhood of attackers success
Security - Likelyhood of escape
Visibility - Likelyhood of attack
Comfort - Player and party comfort in lair

Hot <--Temperature--> Cold
Comfortable <--Habitability--> Stressfull
Dark <--Light Levels--> Bright
Dry <--Humidity--> Moist
None <--Chemicals--> Heady

Terms used in colony animal nests
(wasps, bees, ants, molerate, termites)
-Hatchery
-Trash room
-Ventilation shaft
-Nursery
-Brood chamber
-Queens chamber
-Storage chamber
-Egg room

Terms for caves
Cavern	Cavity	Grotto	Pit
Tunnel	Vault	Cleft	Nest
Sanctuary	Shelter	Sanctum	Cloister
Antechamber	Burrow	Haunt	Nest
Refuge	Hideout


